citation.case_name: The Fisheries Products Company, Receivers of the Fisheries Products Company v. Abraham S. See & Depew, Inc.

html:
269 U.S. 566

46 S.Ct. 24

70 L.Ed. 415

The FISHERIES PRODUCTS COMPANY et al., Receivers of The Fisheries Products Company, petitioners,
v.
ABRAHAM S. SEE & DEPEW, Inc.*

No. 644.

Supreme Court of the United States

October 19, 1925

Mr. T. D. Warren, of Newbern, N. C., for petitioners.

1

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

*

No opinion filed below on order sought to be reviewed, but see 5 F.(2d) 1011, and 9 F.(2d) 235, for other phases of same litigation.
